<img src="/images/concst.png" style="width:100% " />
<div class="container">
    <h1 style="text-align:center;">Convenience Store</h1>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="section-title text-center">Discover Our Amazing Convenience Store</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>You can get more than your prescriptions filled when you visit Bear Creek Pharmacy. Improve your health with our huge selection of vitamins. If you’re experiencing joint or muscle pain, you can choose from a huge selection of pain relievers we carry at our store. We also have first-aid kits and accessories.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="section-title text-center">Stop a Cold in Its Tracks</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>Don't suffer with a cold and hope that it just goes away on its own. At Bear Creek Pharmacy, we carry a wide range of cold and flu medicines that will clear your head and get you back on your feet. Stop by and ask our pharmacist which medicine is right for you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="section-title text-center">Hygiene Care</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>Whether you're looking to keep your skin clean and acne free, or are just looking to eliminate wrinkles, stop by and see us today. We carry a wide selection of hygienic treatment options. Stop by and find the one that is right for you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <video width="320" height="240" controls>
                        <source src="~/videos/bear-creek-pharmacy-llc-jbfpf8zz.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    </video>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>